name: Why Are You Here?
description:
Happy to have 3,000 followers on twitter! Never thought that I could pursue my life's calling as an artist, really, thank you for all the support and love! 

It's just sometimes I wonder...why are you following me? I mean, there are so many great artists out there that worth to follow and I'm surely not one of them. I'll be forever an amateur and my art will always be simple (even extremely simple sometimes lol).

Nonetheless, enjoy this celebratory artwork! Be happy always!
